      <title>尼日利亚扩大美元使用范围，奈拉持续保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/nigeria-extends-dollar-access-as-naira-shows-ongoing-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于当地流动性改善，推动近期奈拉上涨，尼日利亚央行已将外汇局的美元使用期限延长了四个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/nigeria-extends-dollar-access-as-naira-shows-ongoing-stability</guid>
