      <title>特朗普想要为美国设立主权财富基金。它们是什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-wants-a-sovereign-wealth-fund-for-the-us-what-is-an-swf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[主权财富基金是世界上最强大和最神秘的投资者之一，估计其账户中有超过 13 万亿美元。它们由不同国家的政府实体管理，以签发金融领域最大笔款项而闻名，有时也成为巨大丑闻的源头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-05/trump-wants-a-sovereign-wealth-fund-for-the-us-what-is-an-swf</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 12:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
